  "summary": "Malicious code in notify-utilities (npm)",
  "details": "Package is a trojanized clone of the pino logger. When required by an application, index.js spawns a detached background Node.js process (lib/vcall.js) that fetches arbitrary JavaScript code from hxxps://api[.]jsonsilo[.]com/public/df71fd55-4f0c-4326-9b5b-a285e38023a5 and executes it via the Function constructor with access to require(), enabling the remote server to deliver any second-stage payload at will. The package ships a.env file referencing hxxp://vercel-five-coral[.]vercel[.]app/ as a development endpoint.",
